    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronic features are fully functional. While the interior is clean and smoke-free, you may find some light wear on the driver's seat and a few minor surface scratches on the exterior paint consistent with regular use. It\u2019s a reliable, solid car that\u2019s ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
